name: Khurafatti Cat aka Master of Mischief
description:
Khurafatti Cat is the Master of Mischief. No one knows the art of teasing and tricking better than this one. Nonetheless, she is never mean, albeit her jests always have a kernel of truth to them. 50% truth and 50% banter you could say. It is up to you to figure out which is which.

#1 of the Emoji Cat collection: 

Emoji Cat has all the emotions - from innocent to mischievous, you can find them all. This collection is inspired by the unique characters of our feline friends.
